parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can cause the passenger to become trapped in the vehicle, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an emergency.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle gets stuck and won't release
the seat belt buckle is difficult to release
the seat belt buckle is stuck in a position that makes it hard to exit the vehicle
the seat belt buckle randomly comes undone while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt latch can cause the seat belt to not secure properly, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt latch does not release the buckle easily
the seat belt latch sticks in place
the seat belt buckle does not always lock into the latch
the system warning light comes on to notify of an unsecured seat belt.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Seat Belt Recall and Repair Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in repairing or replacing faulty seat belts can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Delay in receiving replacement parts
unreasonable wait time for repair
manufacturer recall issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt warning system can cause the driver to be unaware of an unsecured seat belt, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt warning light does not stay on for 60 seconds when the seat belt is not fastened.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door locking mechanism can cause inconvenience and potential security risks, as the vehicle cannot be locked or unlocked remotely, and manual locking/unlocking is required.
symptoms: Unable to lock or unlock the passenger side door remotely
manual locking/unlocking required from the rear passenger side door.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Park Assist and Rear Camera Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the park assist and rear camera can increase the risk of accidents or damage to the vehicle, as the driver may not be able to accurately judge distances or see obstacles.
symptoms: Park assist system does not work
rear camera not functioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The software glitch causing battery drain can lead to unexpected vehicle shutdowns, stranding the driver, and potentially causing accidents or safety risks.
symptoms: Low battery warning
battery drain
vehicle shutdown
automatic shutdown of accessories to conserve power
repeated battery replacements.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning blind spot assistance system can increase the risk of accidents or damage to the vehicle, as the driver may not be aware of vehicles in the blind spot.
symptoms: Blind spot assistance system camera malfunctioning
error message appears
requires vehicle restart to resolve.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the key ignition switch can cause inconvenience and potentially strand the driver, as the key may become stuck in the ignition switch.
symptoms: Key fails to release from the ignition switch without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield seal can cause water to leak into the cabin, leading to damage to electrical components, corrosion, and mold growth, which can compromise vehicle safety and lead to unpleasant odors and health issues.
symptoms: Water leaking into the cabin
water accumulation on the floor
constant dripping of water on the driver's side of the windshield
water dripping onto the steering wheel
wet and damp smell in the car.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the low battery icon can indicate a battery or electrical system issue, which can cause the vehicle to stall or leave the driver stranded, potentially leading to accidents or safety risks.
symptoms: Low battery icon appears on the dashboard.
